"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Ray Nasser, CEO of Arthur Mining, said that if Brazil passes the tax exemption on crypto miners, it could become a global “Mecca of mining”.\\n\\nUnder the condition that cryptocurrency becomes a legal currency, the Central Bank of Brazil would be allowed to issue a digital real central bank digital currency (CBDC). This would put Brazil among [nine other countries](https://cointelegraph.com/news/eastern-caribbean-cbdc-expands-to-another-two-territories) or jurisdictions that currently issue CBDC to its residents.\\n\\nBrazil currently produces just under [half](https://www.trade.gov/country-commercial-guides/brazil-energy) of its electricity from renewable sources, according to the International Trade Administration. The cost per kilowatt hour is about [$0.12](https://www.globalpetrolprices.com/Brazil/electricity_prices/), putting it roughly in the middle of the global pack in that regard.\",\"timestamp\":1639140006,\"title\":\"the digital economy, and industrial and supply chain integration, Wu Peng said.\"},\"digest\":\"2M0RtlTwNnQ8Gy1IPy7oqhJ_x5krdKvtkm0ppvEEjb4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x748Aed1c03fe0656840e3AfC96d8CDAB1D8717Ec\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Tj18QMQRr8L6D9PN55kSeNRUxT7cRwkG7GtNnTjSqqk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yQmqS_fPRJ2IyMF8IC2ggtj4xjUa2vRDZuL_rV_ZEG0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"C9LrEx_ZnYVmdnaStvIQN3Oj9LdgxaiG9g_lVHj17MSy-UbEM9h1GPnqEJfNHt64N0mJS5uBv1h7DSV-4O_eVQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xff8d804800d6af1d15677a60531a5411bf79d9f0bd8b0fbe4fda81b34b94ea7375ba79903c7a7e242ca92d16c8f5455dbe1ce7adb2850511e74f1337e09ac62c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Tj18QMQRr8L6D9PN55kSeNRUxT7cRwkG7GtNnTjSqqk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yQmqS_fPRJ2IyMF8IC2ggtj4xjUa2vRDZuL_r